### Generated assets ###
# Assets are generated by asset-generator module during backend build:
#   asset-specs/*.xml → backend/target/generated-assets/ → classpath:assets/
# Backend serves via:
#   /assets/** (static PNG/atlas)
#   /api/v1/assets/configs/{type}/{id} (sprite-atlas.json)
# Frontend loads from backend via Vite proxy (dev) or Spring Boot (prod).
# DO NOT commit generated-assets/ — regenerated on every build.

